    title: "7 Onam Traditions You Probably Didn't Know About",
    excerpt: "Beyond the sadya and pookalam, Onam has some fascinating lesser-known traditions that have been passed down through generations — and they deserve to be remembered.",
    seoTitle: "7 Onam Traditions You Didn't Know About | WishSpark Blog",
    seoDescription: "Discover 7 lesser-known Onam traditions from Onakalikal games to Pulikali satire and Vallamkali rituals. Explore the hidden cultural depth of Kerala's biggest festival.",
    seoKeywords: ["Onam traditions", "lesser-known Onam customs", "Onam festival Kerala", "Pulikali history", "Vallamkali boat race", "Onakalikal games", "King Mahabali story", "Onam celebration traditions"],
