    slug: "history-of-greeting-cards",
    title: "From Paper to Pixels: A History of Greeting Cards",
    excerpt: "Greeting cards have survived every technological shift for 600 years. Here's the full story — from a French duke's prison letter to interactive digital wishes.",
    seoTitle: "History of Greeting Cards: From Paper to Digital | WishSpark",
    seoDescription: "Explore the complete history of greeting cards from 1415 to 2026. Learn how handwritten notes evolved into mass-produced cards, e-cards, and interactive digital greetings.",
    seoKeywords: ["history of greeting cards", "greeting card history", "evolution of greeting cards", "digital greeting cards", "first greeting card", "Hallmark history", "e-cards history", "interactive digital greetings"],
    date: "February 18, 2026",
