    seoKeywords: ["republic day india", "january 26 celebration", "indian constitution", "republic day parade", "dr ambedkar constitution", "fundamental rights india", "kartavya path parade", "republic day traditions", "indian democracy", "republic day wishes"],
    excerpt: "January 26th commemorates the moment India became a sovereign democratic republic. Here's what that actually means and why it matters.",
