    title: "Ugadi Meaning and Rituals: A New Year of Balance and Intention",
    seoTitle: "Ugadi 2026: Pachadi Meaning, Home Rituals & New Year Celebration Guide",
    seoDescription: "Explore Ugadi traditions — six-taste pachadi symbolism, panchanga shravanam, mango leaf toranalu, Bevu-Bella, regional foods, and how to celebrate the Telugu-Kannada New Year at home.",
    seoKeywords: ["ugadi 2026", "ugadi pachadi meaning", "ugadi rituals", "telugu new year", "kannada new year", "ugadi celebration", "bevu bella", "panchanga shravanam", "ugadi food traditions", "ugadi greetings"],
    excerpt: "Ugadi celebrations combine prayer, fresh beginnings, and symbolic food that represents the full range of life experiences.",
    date: "March 31, 2026",
    updatedDate: "April 11, 2026",
    author: "Rahul Menon",
